name: SND Transfer
query:
select 
se.name as "Stock Entry Name" ,
se.posting_date as "Entry Date",
sed.item_code as "Item Code",
sed.item_name as "Item Name",
sed.qty as "Quantity",
sed.batch_no as "Batch No" ,
sed.s_warehouse as "Source WH",
sed.t_warehouse as "Target WH",
se.remark as "Remarks"
from 
`tabStock Entry` as se join `tabStock Entry Detail` as sed on sed.parent=se.name 
where 
se.stock_entry_type='Material Transfer' and se.docstatus = 1 and se.reason='SND Transfer' and se.company=%(company)s and
se.posting_date>=%(from_date)s and se.posting_date<=%(to_date)s;
